###############################################
# Employee Management - GET Operations
###############################################

### Get All Employees
GET {{ScmDesignli_HostAddress}}/api/employees
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Employee by ID (existing)
GET {{ScmDesignli_HostAddress}}/api/employees/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Employee by ID (non-existent)
GET {{ScmDesignli_HostAddress}}/api/employees/999
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Employees Paginated (default: page 1, size 10)
GET {{ScmDesignli_HostAddress}}/api/employees/paginated
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Employees Paginated (page 1, size 2)
GET {{ScmDesignli_HostAddress}}/api/employees/paginated?page=1&pageSize=2
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Employees Paginated with Search
GET {{ScmDesignli_HostAddress}}/api/employees/paginated?searchTerm=Juan
Accept: application/json

